WEBVTT

00:04:29.438 --> 00:04:33.282
and illegal wildlife trade are decimating
global wildlife populations.

00:04:33.306 --> 00:04:37.242
We urgently need to create
safe space for these wild animals.

00:04:37.766 --> 00:04:39.511
So in late 2014,

00:04:39.535 --> 00:04:42.116
we launched an ambitious
project to do just that:

00:04:42.140 --> 00:04:43.877
explore and protect.

00:04:44.472 --> 00:04:46.397
By mid-May 2015,

00:04:46.421 --> 00:04:48.750
we had pioneered access
through active minefields

00:04:48.774 --> 00:04:51.417
to the undocumented source lake
of the Cuito River --

00:04:51.441 --> 00:04:53.541
this otherworldly place;

00:04:53.565 --> 00:04:55.525
an ancient, untouched wilderness.

00:04:56.385 --> 00:04:57.680
By the 21st of May,

00:04:57.704 --> 00:05:01.013
we had launched
the Okavango megatransect ...